channel.title: Rune evo v3 commands? new at codding
channel.description: I was just wondering what are some admin commands for evo v3? Also where can I find commands or add new commands? The server doesnt have commands.java so idk where else they would be? Last I was screwing around and typed "admin god" and it gave me like 3m life and idk how to get rid of it. Any help would be appreciated

item.title: Rune evo v3 commands? new at codding
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

Again, rune-evo v3 is crap.
the commands should be located in com.rs.game.player.content.commands;
There are 5 ranks (so 5 files).
Administrator, Donator, Moderator, Owner, Regular, and WikiEditor. Edit the files appropriately.
